latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hi Friends, after a while, the next update is for The Makeup Journey Semman Salai! After your overwhelming responses for the project’s cover song, we are so glad to publish the video! What’s in it for you?! Just a makeup stuff?! Nope, it’s more than just Makeup! It’s to bring out their emotions and feelings about it! How did the model feel when she was dolled up, what was her parents reaction to it! Did they enjoy! Were they happy! Did they react emotionally?! Let’s watch the movie of exclusive coverage from The Makeup Journey to Semman Salai tonight at 9pm! Stay tuned!!! 
@kannanraajamanickam
